# Supabase/PostgreSQL Backend Guidelines

* NEVER create migrations files. The development process is with declaritive schema. ALWAYS edit the schemas instead.
* NEVER create migrations with db diff. the user will do this.
* NEVER run supabase commands. the user will do this.

